  "text": "Following thawing, a 2 ml aliquot of culture media was removed from embryo culture drops and diluted 1:12.5 in HPLC-grade water. Embryofree control drops incubated alongside the embryo drops were treated in the same manner to allow for any non-specific amino acid degradation/appearance. Analysis of 18 amino acids was performed using HPLC as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
